ActAppropriation Act No. 2, 2008-2009
PrecisAppointment of PHILIPPE BEAULNE as Ambassador Extraordinary and Plenipotentiary of Canada to Romania, with concurrent accreditation to the Republic of Bulgaria, and as High Commissioner for Canada to the Republic of Cyprus; WILLIAM CROSBIE as Ambassador Extraordinary and Plenipotentiary of Canada to the Islamic Republic of Afghanistan; STEPHEN HALLIHAN as High Commissioner for Canada to Jamaica, with concurrent accreditation to the Commonwealth of the Bahamas; JOHN HANNAFORD as Ambassador Extraordinary and Plenipotentiary of Canada to the Kingdom of Norway; MARVIN HILDEBRAND as Consul General of Canada in Mumbai, Republic of India; and RON HOFFMANN as Ambassador Extraordinary and Plenipotentiary of Canada to the Kingdom of Thailand.
